<plot>A short film about the grieving process of a loved one, told through the story of a soldier after returning home on leave from the Middle East. As he tries to cope with the loss and memories of what was, he is haunted by his experiences of war through PTS. This disorder and his experiences lead him to a violent confrontation in which he finally confronts all his anguish.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?327984</url></doc>
